        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\tChange your cover photoUpload Change your cover photoUpload\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tApply\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t Cancel\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAnthony Allan\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tThis user account status is Approved\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAbout\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAbout\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPosts\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPosts\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tComments\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tComments\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\tThis user has not added any information to their profile yet.Member TypeStudentE-mail Addressanthony.allan422@gmail.comPhone Number9053201378Design Discipline(s)Lighting, SoundPreferred Pronoun(s)He/HimResidence — Province/TerritoryOntarioLanguages SpokenEnglishResidence — RegionTorontoInstagramInstagramBio\n\n\n\nAs a theatre artist, Anthony (He/Him) is eager to collaborate and advocate for himself and other artists looking to create. As a technical director and designer, he looks to make space and promote an enriching environment for others. He is a recent graduate of the National Theatre School of Canada from the Production Design and Technical Arts program.\nAnthony is looking forward to creating meaningful work for the disadvantaged in our community and promoting representation of all kinds. He is excited to learn and continue to grow in the Canadian theatre industry as it grows more and more diverse.\nWhile at NTS, Anthony has worked on Middletown (Technical Director), Metamorphoses (Sound Designer), the New Words Festival (Lighting Designer), Maybe Not Tomorrow (Production Manager), as well as other management and head of department positions. He has also worked on MASHUP pon di road with Why Not Theatre (Technical Director).\nRelated skills: Vectorworks, Qlab, AutoCAD, ETC EOS programming, Logic Pro X, Microsoft Office Suite\n\n\n\nAvailable for Work?YesAvailable for Assistant/Associate WorkYes\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t.um-113.um {\n\t\t\tmax-width: 1000px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-body {\n\t\t\tmax-width: 600px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-photo a.um-profile-photo-img {\n\t\twidth: 190px;\n\t\theight: 190px;\n\t}\n\t.um-113.um .um-profile-photo a.um-profile-photo-img {\n\t\ttop: -105px;\n\t}\n\t\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-meta {\n\t\t\tpadding-left: 250px;\n\t\t}\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t"
