        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\tChange your cover photoUpload Change your cover photoUpload\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tApply\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t Cancel\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSkye Anderson\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBanner photo features dance and choreography by Bennett Richardson (@bennettrichy) and photography by Jeremy Mimnagh (jeremy@mimnagh.ca).\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tThis user account status is Approved\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAbout\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAbout\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPosts\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPosts\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tComments\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tComments\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\tThis user has not added any information to their profile yet.Member TypeStudentE-mail Addressskye.anderson@torontomu.caWebsite URLhttps://skyecelialee.myportfolio.com/Phone Number5194778121Design Discipline(s)LightingPreferred Pronoun(s)She/HerResidence — Province/TerritoryOntarioLanguages SpokenEnglish, FrenchResidence — RegionTorontoBioSkye Celia Lee Anderson is a fourth year student in Toronto Metropolitan University's Performance: Production program (née Ryerson Theatre School). Skye has had the privilege of working with artists across Dance, Drama and Beyond including Dancetheatre David Earle, Rick Miller, Kris Alexander and Côté Danse. When she's not in the theatre, Skye avidly watches the TTC vehicles that pass her by, hoping to someday add each and every cardboard model to her collection. \n \nAvailable for Work?YesAvailable for Assistant/Associate WorkYes\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t.um-113.um {\n\t\t\tmax-width: 1000px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-body {\n\t\t\tmax-width: 600px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-photo a.um-profile-photo-img {\n\t\twidth: 190px;\n\t\theight: 190px;\n\t}\n\t.um-113.um .um-profile-photo a.um-profile-photo-img {\n\t\ttop: -105px;\n\t}\n\t\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-meta {\n\t\t\tpadding-left: 250px;\n\t\t}\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t"
