        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\tChange your cover photoUpload Change your cover photoUpload\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tApply\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t Cancel\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLucas Arab\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tScenic Designer, Make-Believer\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tThis user account status is Approved\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAbout\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAbout\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPosts\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPosts\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tComments\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tComments\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\tThis user has not added any information to their profile yet.Member TypeAssociate MemberE-mail Addresslucas@lucasarab.comWebsite URLhttp://lucasarab.comDesign Discipline(s)Scenery, VideoPreferred Pronoun(s)he/him/hisResidence — Province/TerritoryNova ScotiaLanguages SpokenEnglish, FrenchInstagramInstagramLinkedInLinkedInBioI consider myself to be a \"professional make-believer\" with the goal of creating immersive and visually intriguing storytelling spaces for all. My work is focused in collaboration and imagination, and I believe that strong design has the ability to change the world. I hold a Bachelor of Arts with Honours in Stage Design and Technical Theatre. I am a Canadian designer based in Halifax, Nova Scotia.\n \nWhen I am not designing for the stage, I am the Education Content Creator at Neptune Theatre School, creating and overseeing programs that directly engage youth in theatre. I am also the Co-Regional Producer of the Canadian Improv Games in Nova Scotia. \nAvailable for Work?YesAvailable for Assistant/Associate WorkYes\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t.um-113.um {\n\t\t\tmax-width: 1000px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-body {\n\t\t\tmax-width: 600px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-photo a.um-profile-photo-img {\n\t\twidth: 190px;\n\t\theight: 190px;\n\t}\n\t.um-113.um .um-profile-photo a.um-profile-photo-img {\n\t\ttop: -105px;\n\t}\n\t\t\t.um-113.um .um-profile-meta {\n\t\t\tpadding-left: 250px;\n\t\t}\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t"
